Tata Sons Buys Shares in Cars, Steel Units From Tata Chemicals

-- B y   J e a n e t t e   R o d r i g u e s
-- 
2011-09-05T14:32:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-05/tata-sons-buys-shares-in-cars-steel-units-from-tata-chemicals.html
Tata Sons Ltd. raised its stake in
 Tata Motors Ltd. (TTMT)  and  Tata Steel Ltd. (TATA)  by buying some shares held
by Tata Chemicals Ltd. in the two companies, according to a
filing on the Bombay Stock Exchange today.  Tata Sons bought 331,000 Tata Motors shares at 750 rupees
each and 510,000 Tata Steel shares at 483.50 rupees each from
Tata Chemicals, the filing showed.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeanette Rodrigues in Mumbai at 
 jrodrigues26@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Abhay Singh at 
 abhaysingh@bloomberg.net  